Setup up Geotagger project in Eclipse
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Precondition
------------
1. Android SDK is setup in Eclipse.
 - If not, set Android SDK path via Window->Preferences, and then select Android from the left menu. Add the path to the SDK location.
2. An AVD is created with API level 8 (platform 2.2).
 - If not, create one via e.g. AVD manager.

Instructions
------------
1. Create new Android Project
2. Select "create project from existing source" and specify the path to Geotagger repository and press Finish.
